---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Dashboard" description="sentrik's built-in management dashboard — findings, rules, policies, work items, and audit log in one web UI.">

<section class="dash-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Management Dashboard</h1>
    <p class="dash-sub">A built-in web UI for managing findings, rules, governance policies, work items, and audit trails. No separate install — it ships with sentrik.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="dash-start">
  <div class="container dash-start-inner">
    <pre><code>npm install -g sentrik
sentrik dashboard</code></pre>
    <p>The sentrik dashboard opens automatically in an app window.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="dash-tabs">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Everything You Need. One Dashboard.</h2>
    <div class="tabs-grid">

      <div class="tab-card">
        <div class="tab-icon">&#x1F4CA;</div>
        <h3>Overview</h3>
        <p>Scan metrics at a glance — severity breakdown, top files, scan duration, cache hit rate, and findings-over-time trend chart.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tab-card">
        <div class="tab-icon">&#x1F50D;</div>
        <h3>Findings</h3>
        <p>Searchable, filterable list of all findings with severity, rule ID, file location, and remediation guidance. Click to expand details.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tab-card">
        <div class="tab-icon">&#x1F4C4;</div>
        <h3>Reports</h3>
        <p>Generate and download HTML, JUnit XML, SARIF, and CSV reports. One click for audit-ready artifacts.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tab-card">
        <div class="tab-icon">&#x1F6E1;</div>
        <h3>Policies</h3>
        <p>Configure governance profiles (strict, standard, permissive), human review gates, auto-patch settings, and gate thresholds.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tab-card">
        <div class="tab-icon">&#x1F4E6;</div>
        <h3>Packs</h3>
        <p>Enable, disable, and configure standards packs. Override individual rules within a pack. Import and export custom packs (Enterprise).</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tab-card">
        <div class="tab-icon">&#x1F4CB;</div>
        <h3>Rules</h3>
        <p>Browse all active rules with severity, type (regex, AST, file policy), and auto-fix status. Search and filter across packs.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tab-card">
        <div class="tab-icon">&#x1F3AF;</div>
        <h3>Work Items</h3>
        <p>View linked Azure DevOps, GitHub, or Jira work items. Reconcile findings — auto-create, update, and close items.</p>
        <span class="team-badge">Team</span>
      </div>

      <div class="tab-card">
        <div class="tab-icon">&#x1F517;</div>
        <h3>Integration</h3>
        <p>Connect to Azure DevOps, GitHub, or Jira. Test connections, configure OAuth, and see environment variable status.</p>
        <span class="team-badge">Team</span>
      </div>

      <div class="tab-card">
        <div class="tab-icon">&#x1F4DC;</div>
        <h3>Audit Log</h3>
        <p>Timestamped log of every scan, gate, reconcile, and config change. Filter by action type. Export for compliance evidence.</p>
        <span class="enterprise-badge">Enterprise</span>
      </div>

      <div class="tab-card">
        <div class="tab-icon">&#x2705;</div>
        <h3>Approvals</h3>
        <p>Async approval gates for enterprise workflows. Review pending requests, approve or reject, track timeout and status.</p>
        <span class="enterprise-badge">Enterprise</span>
      </div>

      <div class="tab-card">
        <div class="tab-icon">&#x2699;</div>
        <h3>Settings</h3>
        <p>Full configuration viewer and editor. Validate config, toggle features, and manage output paths — all from the browser.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="dash-screenshots">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">See It In Action</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Real screenshots from a medical device API project scanned with 4 standards packs (IEC 62304, HIPAA, OWASP, SOC2).</p>

    <div class="screenshot-gallery">
      <div class="screenshot-item">
        <img src="/images/dash-overview.png" alt="Dashboard overview — compliance score, severity chart, scan metrics" class="screenshot" loading="lazy" />
        <p class="screenshot-label">Overview &mdash; 100% compliance score, severity breakdown, scan trends</p>
      </div>
      <div class="screenshot-item">
        <img src="/images/dash-findings.png" alt="Findings list with severity, rule ID, and descriptions" class="screenshot" loading="lazy" />
        <p class="screenshot-label">Findings &mdash; searchable list with severity, rule ID, and remediation guidance</p>
      </div>
      <div class="screenshot-item">
        <img src="/images/dash-vulnerabilities.png" alt="Vulnerability scan showing CVEs in dependencies" class="screenshot" loading="lazy" />
        <p class="screenshot-label">Vulnerabilities &mdash; CVE scan results with severity and fix versions</p>
      </div>
      <div class="screenshot-item">
        <img src="/images/dash-rules.png" alt="Active rules browser with severity and type filters" class="screenshot" loading="lazy" />
        <p class="screenshot-label">Rules &mdash; browse all active rules by severity, type, and standard</p>
      </div>
      <div class="screenshot-item">
        <img src="/images/dash-packs.png" alt="Standards packs management" class="screenshot" loading="lazy" />
        <p class="screenshot-label">Packs &mdash; enable, disable, and configure standards packs</p>
      </div>
      <div class="screenshot-item">
        <img src="/images/dash-work-items.png" alt="Work items synced from GitHub Issues" class="screenshot" loading="lazy" />
        <p class="screenshot-label">Work Items &mdash; synced GitHub Issues with requirement traceability</p>
      </div>
      <div class="screenshot-item">
        <img src="/images/dash-policies.png" alt="Governance policies configuration" class="screenshot" loading="lazy" />
        <p class="screenshot-label">Policies &mdash; governance profiles, human review gates, auto-patch controls</p>
      </div>
      <div class="screenshot-item">
        <img src="/images/dash-audit-log.png" alt="Audit log with HMAC integrity signatures" class="screenshot" loading="lazy" />
        <p class="screenshot-label">Audit Log &mdash; every scan, gate, and reconcile event with HMAC integrity</p>
      </div>
      <div class="screenshot-item">
        <img src="/images/dash-history.png" alt="Historical scan runs with trend analysis" class="screenshot" loading="lazy" />
        <p class="screenshot-label">History &mdash; historical scan runs with finding trends over time</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3 class="section-title" style="margin-top:3rem">AI Chat &amp; Vulnerability Triage</h3>
    <div class="screenshot-gallery">
      <div class="screenshot-item">
        <img src="/images/ai-chat-panel-1.png" alt="AI Chat — understanding a finding" class="screenshot" loading="lazy" />
        <p class="screenshot-label">Fix with AI &mdash; chat with an LLM about any finding</p>
      </div>
      <div class="screenshot-item">
        <img src="/images/vuln-chat-1.png" alt="Vulnerability scan with AI chat" class="screenshot" loading="lazy" />
        <p class="screenshot-label">Vulnerability Chat &mdash; AI explains CVE impact on your code</p>
      </div>
      <div class="screenshot-item">
        <img src="/images/vuln-chat-2.png" alt="AI explains vulnerability fix" class="screenshot" loading="lazy" />
        <p class="screenshot-label">Understand Before You Upgrade &mdash; AI checks for breaking changes</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="dash-features">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Built-In Features</h2>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-item">
        <h3>Dark Mode</h3>
        <p>Light and dark themes with one-click toggle. Preference saved in localStorage.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <h3>Global Search</h3>
        <p>Press <code>Ctrl+K</code> to search across findings, rules, and work items instantly.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <h3>Keyboard Shortcuts</h3>
        <p>Press <code>?</code> for the help overlay. Navigate tabs, trigger scans, and copy data without touching the mouse.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <h3>REST API</h3>
        <p>25+ API endpoints power the dashboard. Use them directly for CI/CD integration, custom tooling, or remote scanning.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <h3>Live Scan Progress</h3>
        <p>Server-Sent Events stream scan progress in real time. Watch files being processed as they happen.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-item">
        <h3>Scan Trends</h3>
        <p>SVG line chart showing findings over time. Track whether your codebase is getting cleaner or accumulating debt.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="dash-cta">
  <div class="container dash-cta-inner">
    <h2>Try it now</h2>
    <pre><code>npm install -g sentrik && sentrik dashboard</code></pre>
    <div class="cta-actions">
      <a href="/blog/getting-started-in-5-minutes" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
      <a href="/pricing" class="btn btn-outline">View Pricing</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Base>

<style>
  .screenshot { width: 100%; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .dash-screenshots { padding: 3rem 0; }
  .section-sub { text-align: center; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .screenshot-gallery { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
  .screenshot-item { }
  .screenshot-item .screenshot { transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; cursor: pointer; }
  .screenshot-item .screenshot:hover { transform: scale(1.02); box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
  .screenshot-label { text-align: center; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem; margin-top: 0.75rem; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .screenshot-gallery { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
  @media (max-width: 600px) { .screenshot-gallery { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .dash-hero { padding: 6rem 0 3rem; text-align: center; }
  .dash-sub { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 1.2rem; margin-top: 1rem; max-width: 700px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }

  .dash-start { padding: 0 0 3rem; text-align: center; }
  .dash-start-inner pre { display: inline-block; padding: 0.75rem 2rem; font-size: 1.05rem; border: 2px solid var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .dash-start-inner p { color: var(--color-text-muted); }

  .section-title { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; }

  .tabs-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
  .tab-card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .tab-icon { font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .tab-card h3 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.15rem; }
  .tab-card p { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; margin: 0; }
  .enterprise-badge, .team-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1rem;
    right: 1rem;
    padding: 0.15rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .enterprise-badge { background: var(--color-primary); }
  .team-badge { background: #2563eb; }

  .dash-features { background: var(--color-bg-alt); }
  .features-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
  .feature-item {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  .feature-item h3 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem; }
  .feature-item p { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; margin: 0; }

  .dash-cta { text-align: center; }
  .dash-cta h2 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .dash-cta pre { display: inline-block; padding: 0.75rem 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 1rem; }
  .cta-actions { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .tabs-grid, .features-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .cta-actions { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
  }
</style>
